            "indent": 0,
            "type": "link",
            "rel": null,
            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "__GHOST_URL__/articles/news/dodge-future-muscle-car-plans/",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " for all the giant automaker’s vehicles (get ready for the Fiat 500 Hellcat) many enthusiasts are skeptical if not downright furious. Likely to help calm everyone down, the head of design at Stellantis, ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
